<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MTA48">
<l>kaḻaloṉ ṟeṭuttorukai cuṟṟiyōr kaimēṟ</l>
<l>cuḻaluñ curācurarka ḷañca – vaḻaluñ</l>
<l>ceruvāḻi yēntiṉāṉ cēvaṭikkē cella</l>
<l>maruvāḻi neñcē makiḻ</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Join in going to the red feet of him who held up the flaming battle discus</l>
<l>on one hand, for the agitated gods and Asuras to be afraid,</l>
<l>with the other hand lifting [Namuci] by one foot [and] spinning [him] around.</l>
<l>Immerse yourself in joy, heart!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
